0\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br />\r\nXe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ee9t x\u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc El Tri<br />\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 (th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch), nh\u01b0ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Joachim Loew \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 ngay tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Mexico, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00cdt ng\u00e0y sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng c\u0169ng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m l\u1ea1c quan, nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f3 m\u1eb7c to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico \" title=\"Boateng vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/sao-tuyen-duc-thua-nhan-chien-thuat-sai-lam-trong-tran-thua-mexico.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng&nbsp;l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;V\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u1edf m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a khi \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn, ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/thuy-dien-vs-han-quoc-bang-f-463-188813.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span>, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo, Boateng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh k\u1ebb ch\u1ea7u r\u00eca ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Manuel Neuer cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang mong ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t SV\u0110 m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. R\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng.&rdquo;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Boateng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lozano-ghi-ban-ha-guc-duc-mot-cdv-mexico-bat-ngo-lay-duoc-vo-421-188930.html\">Lozano ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110\u1ee9c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ee3</span><br />\r\nQu\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V Mexico c\u1ea7u h\u00f4n b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i ngay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dkvd-thua-soc-ngay-ra-quan-low-da-thuc-su-het-bai-421-188808.html\">\u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n: Low \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ebft b\u00e0i?</span><br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng ai mong ch\u1edd \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/lozano.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-duc-vs-mexico-bang-f-world-cup-2018-h1-461-188750.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 0-1 Mexico (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 ra qu\u00e2n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 khoa h\u1ecdc. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"380","checkdouble":"189012"},{"date":"10:47 20/06","title":"Pepe: \"Ronaldo t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u1ea7m \u0129\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/pepe-ronaldo-toa-sang-co-gi-ma-am-i.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u00ecnh \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u201cnh\u00ecn v\u1eady v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Rostov Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Rostov-on-Don)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Uruguay -0.97*0:2*0.91 Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.93*3*0.85 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Saudi Arabia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng A, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. 14 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Celeste \u0111\u01b0a ra song m\u00e3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 89, nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" title=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Gimenez-danh-dau-vao-luoi-Ai-Cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Gimenez ph\u00fat 89</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u01a1i Uruguay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u1ed5ng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 cao to c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Uruguay c\u0169ng phung ph\u00ed. Ri\u00eang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ai C\u1eadp. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t nh\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng Barcelona, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. Anh t\u1ecf ra n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 trong di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay: Salah bu\u1ed3n, Suarez n\u00e0o c\u00f3 vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi Salah bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00e0o ph\u00fat...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1. Uruguay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00edch \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m vui tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Uruguay. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen n\u00e0y. G\u1ea7n 2 n\u0103m qua, Uruguay ch\u01a1i 17 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu l\u1eabn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin gop dau giay vao 3/5 ban thang cua Nga truoc Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Golovin g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/may-bay-cho-tuyen-saudi-arabia-phut-lua-tren-troi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Uruguay th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 tr\u1eadn trong \u0111\u00f3. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn h\u1ecd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh ph\u00e1 &ldquo;b\u00ea t\u00f4ng&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng A l\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 thua thi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (20/6), Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uruguay. Trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng, &ldquo;Chim \u01b0ng xanh&rdquo; s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Uruguay kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH bang A\" title=\"BXH bang A\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/BXH-bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 7/17 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 4/10 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n- Trong 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n, 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: Saudi Arabia (+2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. \u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Uruguay c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 1-0 v\u00e0 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed c\u00f3 s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, xem ra La Celeste c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Tabarez noi ve tran Ai Cap vs Uruguay\" title=\"Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-ai-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV&nbsp;Tabarez \u0111\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 ri\u00eang cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 4 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. H\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n Saudi Arabia, lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n b\u1ecb Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 0-5 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3/15 l\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n. Uruguay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 1/11 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/15 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1:</strong> Uruguay th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 (-4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (-1)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn (-3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"379","checkdouble":"189013"},{"date":"11:02 20/06","title":"\u0110T Anh nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/dt-anh-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-tru-cot.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tusinia, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi Tunisia ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Anh ch\u01a1i ph\u00eda sau b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u00e0 Raheem Sterling. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Tunisia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/dt-anh-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-tru-cot.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 80, Alli ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Ruben Loftus-Cheek, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 Anh \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 Alli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Gareth Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng r\u00fat Alli ra ngh\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, Tam s\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane \u1edf nh\u1eefng\u00a0ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Alli</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tusinia, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Gareth Southgate x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve tran Anh vs Tunisia\" title=\"Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/gareth-southgate-ngoai-kane-cac-chan-sut-con-lai-cua-anh-qua-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Southgate hy v\u1ecdng Alli kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAlli d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au \u1edf \u0111\u00f9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Alli\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Alli s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Alli c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i: \u201cT\u00f4i \u1ed5n. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Panama, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thua B\u1ec9 0-3 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Panama c\u00f2n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng G.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"378","checkdouble":"189015"},{"date":"11:54 20/06","title":"\u0110T B\u1ec9 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/dt-bi-chuan-bi-doi-mat-voi-nguy-co-lon-chua-tung-co.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ngay sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 lo ngay ng\u00e1y c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bi-vs-panama-bang-g-463-188832.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Panama 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1</span>, v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Dries Mertens c\u00f9ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Romelu Lukaku. D\u00f9 ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, B\u1ec9 s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i CLB. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ngay t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra VCK World Cup, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hazard-chelsea-phai-chi-dam-moi-giu-duoc-toi-421-188884.html\" target=\"_blank\">Eden Hazard kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1eadm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh</span>. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung, t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u00f9ng tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia &ndash; \u00f4ng Vital Borkelmans cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Courtois c\u0169ng v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111i. Courtois r\u1ea5t th\u00edch cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Chelse v\u00e0 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c, m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi Fellaini v\u00e0 Alderweireld. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi Fellaini, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, trong khi Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ee7a \u0110T&rdquo; &ndash; c\u1ef1u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV B\u1ec9 chia s\u1ebb n\u1ed7i lo l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bi-30-panama-khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-421-188888.html\">B\u1ec9&hellip; v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Panama: Khi m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi khen \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef &ldquo;nh\u01b0ng&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 3-0 Panama l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u01b0\u1ee3t ra qu\u00e2n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i c\u00e1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ea5t an \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf v\u1eabn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lukaku-lap-ky-luc-ghi-ban-khung-fan-mu-lai-loi-morata-ra-de-biu-421-188880.html\">Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n kh\u1ee7ng, fan M.U l\u1ea1i l\u00f4i&hellip; Morata ra d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110T Panama m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c kh\u1ee7ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bi-30-panama-bang-g-world-cup-2018-461-188867.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama (B\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 c\u00f3 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Mertens v\u00e0 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf gi\u00e0nh th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"377","checkdouble":"189016"},{"date":"10:48 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c cho tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh ai c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u00ecnh \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia c\u1ee7a Bongda24h.vn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ra c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u201cnh\u00ecn v\u1eady v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1eady\u201d.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Rostov Arena (th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Rostov-on-Don)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Uruguay -0.97*0:2*0.91 Saudi Arabia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Nhi\u1ec1u -0.93*3*0.85 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia 22h ng\u00e0y 20/6</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Saudi Arabia</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng A, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay. Trong \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. 14 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c La Celeste \u0111\u01b0a ra song m\u00e3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 89, nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Jose Gimenez xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" title=\"Gimenez danh dau vao luoi Ai Cap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Gimenez-danh-dau-vao-luoi-Ai-Cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Uruguay v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ai C\u1eadp 1-0 nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Gimenez ph\u00fat 89</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc n\u01a1i Uruguay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Oscar Tabarez th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n qua l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u1ed5ng b\u1ecb c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 cao to c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, Uruguay c\u0169ng phung ph\u00ed. Ri\u00eang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ai C\u1eadp. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t nh\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng Barcelona, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ed1 9 c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u1eaft ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. Anh t\u1ecf ra n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 trong di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-salah-buon-suarez-nao-co-vui-gi-421-188597.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp 0-1 Uruguay: Salah bu\u1ed3n, Suarez n\u00e0o c\u00f3 vui g\u00ec</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a hai ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong khi Salah bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 thua v\u00e0o ph\u00fat...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1. Uruguay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00edch \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd th\u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Saudi Arabia, gi\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh ni\u1ec1m vui tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n cho Uruguay. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00f3i quen n\u00e0y. G\u1ea7n 2 n\u0103m qua, Uruguay ch\u01a1i 17 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu l\u1eabn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng c\u00f3 7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin gop dau giay vao 3/5 ban thang cua Nga truoc Saudi Arabia\" title=\"Golovin g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3/5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/may-bay-cho-tuyen-saudi-arabia-phut-lua-tren-troi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Uruguay th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 7 tr\u1eadn trong \u0111\u00f3. C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn h\u1ecd th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh ph\u00e1 &ldquo;b\u00ea t\u00f4ng&rdquo; v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do Tabarez d\u1eabn d\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3. Tr\u00ean BXH b\u1ea3ng A l\u00fac n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 0 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 thua thi\u1ec7t. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ai C\u1eadp r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay (20/6), Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uruguay. Trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng, &ldquo;Chim \u01b0ng xanh&rdquo; s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Uruguay kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH bang A\" title=\"BXH bang A\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/BXH-bang-A.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Saudi Arabia \u0111\u1ee9ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 7/17 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n- Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 4/10 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y<br>\r\n- Trong 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 2 b\u00e0n, 1 tr\u1eadn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: Saudi Arabia (+2)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. \u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Uruguay c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ecd th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i th\u00ec l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t 1-0 v\u00e0 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Gi\u1ea3 s\u1eed c\u00f3 s\u1edbm v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, xem ra La Celeste c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Tabarez noi ve tran Ai Cap vs Uruguay\" title=\"Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ai C\u1eadp vs Uruguay\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-truoc-ai-cap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV&nbsp;Tabarez \u0111\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0 ri\u00eang cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 4 b\u00e0n m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. H\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m qua, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n n\u00e0y. C\u00f2n Saudi Arabia, lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n b\u1ecb Nga h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t 0-5 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3/15 l\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y trong c\u00f9ng th\u1eddi gian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 h\u1ea1n. Uruguay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</em><br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 1/11 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Ch\u1ec9 4/15 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Uruguay c\u00f3 t\u1eeb 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1edf l\u00ean<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 3 tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: \u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (U 3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- <strong>Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t</strong> (t\u1eeb 2 tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1:</strong> Uruguay th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 (O 4)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 5 (-4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 (-2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 (-1)<br>\r\n- S\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn (-3)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"376","checkdouble":"189017"},{"date":"11:00 20/06","title":"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 VTV 20/6","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/lich-truyen-hinh-phat-song-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-vtv-206.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang b\u00e1o b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Fifa World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay 20/6 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0i VTV v\u00e0 HTV v\u00e0 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng internet</h2><table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 VTV 206 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 VTV 206 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/lich-truyen-hinh-phat-song-truc-tiep-world-cup-2018-20-6.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 sung</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp b\u1ea3ng A d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 ng\u0169 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec c\u1ee7a Uruguay v\u00e0 \u0110T Nga. \u0110T Uruguay t\u1ed1i nay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng \u1ea2 R\u1eadp X\u00ea \u00dat. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/16 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nT\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng B, \u0111\u00eam nay s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Morocco v\u00e0 Iran. 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Iran \u0111ang c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean 1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br />\r\n<h3>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup 2018 VTV h\u00f4m nay</h3>\r\n<table width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <colgroup><col style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:6912;width:142pt\" width=\"189\" />  <col style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:3254;width:67pt\" width=\"89\" />  <col style=\"mso-width-source:userset;mso-width-alt:12909;width:265pt\" width=\"353\" />  </colgroup>\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\">\r\n            <td style=\"height: 15pt; width: 142pt; text-align: center;\" width=\"189\" height=\"20\"><strong>TR\u1eacN \u0110\u1ea4U</strong></td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 67pt; text-align: center;\" width=\"89\"><strong>TH\u1edcI GIAN</strong></td>\r\n            <td style=\"width: 265pt; text-align: center;\" width=\"353\"><strong>K\u00caNH PH\u00c1T S\u00d3NG</strong></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\">\r\n            <td style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-bo-dao-nha-vs-maroc-19h00-ngay-206-an-tu-dau-tien-421-188986.htmlabc\" target=\"_blank\" type=\"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Morocco</span></td>\r\n            <td>20/06 19h00</td>\r\n            <td>VTV 6, VTV6 HD, HTV1, HTV TT, HTV4</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\">\r\n            <td style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-va-du-doan-uruguay-vs-saudi-arabia-421-189017.htmlabc\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia\">Uruguay vs Saudi Arabia</span></td>\r\n            <td>20/06 22h00</td>\r\n            <td>VTV 6, VTV6 HD, HTV1, HTV TT, HTV4, , HTV9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\">\r\n            <td style=\"height:15.0pt\" height=\"20\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-1h-ngay-216-boi-la-roja-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-421-188993.htmlabc\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Iran\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Iran</span></td>\r\n            <td>21/06 01h00</td>\r\n            <td>VTV 3, VTV3 HD, HTV1, HTV TT, HTV4 , HTV9, HTV7</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"375","checkdouble":"189021"},{"date":"11:12 20/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 20/6: Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/ngay-hom-nay-206.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (20/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nRonaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Morocco \u0111\u00eam nay, chuy\u00ean gia Mark Lawrenson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0i BBC cho bi\u1ebft: \"B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1edbi Ronaldo - m\u1ed9t chuy\u00ean gia \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 206 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 206 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/world-cup-2018-khi-bong-chet-tro-thanh-vu-khi-chien-luoc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Hierro v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng De Gea sau sai l\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG\u00a0T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh David De Gea v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean: \u201cDe Gea v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu ta gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh, t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi khi. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay World Cup v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">World Cup ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin kh\u00f4ng vui khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Park Joo-ho c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay s\u00e2n c\u1ecf trong 3 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n kheo trong tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1ee9 2 v\u1eeba qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3nh n\u1eb1m c\u00e1ng r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Kim Min-woo ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 28 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen Lukaku</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Lukaku l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. D\u00f9 hi\u1ec7p 1 ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1ed1 9 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Hazard kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00ean m\u00e2y: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ea7n Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0n b\u1ea1c kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Lukaku c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Lukaku s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 \u1edf World Cup 2018\".</div>\r\n<h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Colombia nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f9ng 2 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Colombia \u0111\u00e3 thua s\u1ed1c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Colombia b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00f4i qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 ph\u00fat 56 gi\u00e2y. Sanchez l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf nhanh th\u1ee9 2 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, sau tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Jose Batista n\u0103m 1986 (54 gi\u00e2y).<br>\r\n\u00a0\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-colombia-suyt-lap-ky-luc-ve-thoi-gian-nhan-the-do-tai-world-cup-421-188963.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/sao-colombia-suyt-lap-ky-luc-ve-thoi-gian-nhan-the-do-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-colombia-suyt-lap-ky-luc-ve-thoi-gian-nhan-the-do-tai-world-cup-421-188963.html\">Sao Colombia su\u00fdt l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br>\r\n<span>V\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Carlos Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n nhanh th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 21 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"374","checkdouble":"189023"},{"date":"11:29 20/06","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm Lucas Torreira thay Wilshere</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Jack Wilshere x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eddi Arsenal</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira la mot chien binh dich thuc\" title=\"Lucas Torreira l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn binh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Arsenal-chieu-mo-Torreira-Tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lucas Torreira l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria v\u1edbi 36 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Lucas Torreira, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Torreira</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lucas Torreira th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chieu mo Torreira voi gia 30 trieu euro\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/chu-tich-sampdoria-xac-nhan-ban-sao-khung-cho-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mua c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2015 t\u1eeb Pescara, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Torreira th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Serie A&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecf ra 3 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Torreira, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n 30 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Arsenal s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian. Torreira s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng hai t\u00e2n binh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Bernd Leno.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"373","checkdouble":"189024"},{"date":"11:37 20/06","title":"Chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Senegal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/chieu-tro-phoi-hop-phat-goc-cuc-doc-cua-tuyen-senegal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Senegal v\u1eeba ph\u00e1t minh ra m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c m\u1edbi trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Ba Lan t\u1ed1i qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Senegal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c n\u1eefa \u1edf World Cup 2018 khi gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Ba Lan \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng H. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1edfi h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u00e9n, ma m\u00e3nh c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam ch\u00fat may m\u1eafn trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi c\u00f2n g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1, ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai \u1edf pha d\u00e0n x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Senegal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Khi \u0111\u00f3 \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh quay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh Mame Biram Diouf b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd k\u00e9o \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Salif Sane.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Senegal c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9c, l\u1ea1, ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Senegal c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9c, l\u1ea1, ch\u01b0a xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Senegal.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. Trang Dreamteamfc \u0111\u1eb7t ra gi\u1ea3 thuy\u1ebft Mame Biram Diouf mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng th\u00eam xung l\u1ef1c cho Salif Sane \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eadt cao h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong, c\u1ea7n l\u01b0u \u00fd r\u1eb1ng Salif Sane s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao h\u01a1n 1,9 m. Th\u1eed h\u1ecfi \"m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u00e0o\" nh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u1ea7n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eadt cao h\u01a1n? C\u0169ng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n quan \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eb1ng HLV Aliou Ciss\u00e9 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Senegd\u1ebfnd\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh b\u00e0y ra chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y h\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ec5 ki\u1ebfm penalty h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u1ec3n Senegal th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn hai l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 Diouf lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u00e9o \u00e1o Sane. Chi\u00eau tr\u00f2 l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm n\u00e0y su\u00fdt ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng khi Sane c\u00f3 pha ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c \"\u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o\" c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Senegal, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Diouf k\u00e9o \u00e1o Sane.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-cua-senegal-tiet-lo-ly-do-danh-bai-ba-lan-421-189006.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nguoi-hung-cua-senegal-tiet-lo-ly-do-danh-bai-ba-lan.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-cua-senegal-tiet-lo-ly-do-danh-bai-ba-lan-421-189006.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Senegal ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan</span><br>\r\n<span>Mbaye Niang ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Torino \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng\u201d trong ng\u00e0y...</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal-421-188995.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lewandowski-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-ba-lan-truoc-senegal-421-188995.html\">Lewandowski n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Ba Lan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal</span><br>\r\n<span>Robert Lewandowski ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ba-lan-thua-dau-senegal-boi-su-yeu-kem-cua-trong-tai-421-188991.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ba-lan-thua-dau-senegal-boi-su-yeu-kem-cua-trong-tai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ba-lan-thua-dau-senegal-boi-su-yeu-kem-cua-trong-tai-421-188991.html\">Ba Lan thua \u0111au Senegal b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span><br>\r\n<span>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho Senegal \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb pha c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Niang t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan, l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal-469-188981.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal-469-188981.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Senegal</span><br>\r\n<span>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i El Hadji Diouf c\u1ee7a Senegal \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed Teranga\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ba Lan v\u1eeba qua.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal-421-188976.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal-421-188976.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea3ng H VCK World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span><br>\r\n<span>HLV Aliou Cisse chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o Phi ch\u00e2u sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Senegal tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"372","checkdouble":"189028"},{"date":"07:41 20/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/6): \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2062018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018: Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e0 th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng mang t\u00ean Cristiano Ronaldo, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Bay cao tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 vua Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111ang trong tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u1ecb v\u00ec c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng ng\u1edd v\u1ef1c hay c\u1ea3 ch\u1ebf nh\u1ea1o, tr\u00f9 \u1ebbo. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mu\u00f4n v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1nh gi\u1ec1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh l\u00ec l\u1ee3m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Ph\u00e1p c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1eadt l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc 19h ng\u00e0y 206 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc 19h ng\u00e0y 206 b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-19h-ngay-206-bang-B-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bo-dao-nha-vs-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-463-188575.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3 derby b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea3o Iberia</span> l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i hai l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ec7t ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa hat-trick si\u00eau h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng knock-out cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t, Iran v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft t\u1ed1i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Maroc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-chi-co-the-va-mai-luon-la-anh-cristiano-ronaldo-421-188617.html\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 m\u00e3i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 anh, Cristiano Ronaldo!</span><br>\r\nBa b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng Sochi, Cristiano Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp c\u00fa hat-trick th\u1ee9 51, trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed 88 n\u0103m c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u0169ng nh\u01b0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Iran kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sau ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maroc: T\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t S\u01b0 T\u1eed<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00fang, v\u1edbi c\u00e1nh chim \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0n Ronaldo l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecdc nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi \u1edf ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga (8 b\u00e0n/2 tr\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018). Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nan gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh ra, \u201cBrazil Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\u201d th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t khi \u1edf v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 thi tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Gi\u1edd, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i tr\u00e0n l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Maroc, m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u201cl\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\u201d \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb B\u1eafc Phi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-(19h00-ngay-206)-An-tu-dau-tien-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 70% th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ph\u00fat 90+5 v\u00ec m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean, Maroc kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng knock-out, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t h\u1ecd l\u00e0 hai ng\u1ecdn n\u00fai T\u00e2y \u2013 B\u1ed3. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ed5 t\u00edch s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, Maroc c\u0169ng \u00fd th\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i d\u1ea1i d\u1ed9t d\u00e2ng cao ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 l\u1ed9 ra ph\u00eda sau nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2ng cho Ronaldo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ri\u00eang c\u0169ng v\u1eady, cho n\u00ean HLV Herve Renand s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u201ch\u1ed3i m\u00e3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Iran, Maroc ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi qu\u00e1 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n/tr\u1eadn, v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a n\u01a1i th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Medhi Benatia, ng\u00f4i sao t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u00f3 th\u1eeba.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Bo Dao Nha vs Maroc\" title=\"Preview B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u01b0 T\u1eed Atlas \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft v\u00ec h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho h\u1ecd trong m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t sinh t\u1eed. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m v\u00ec 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i canh b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n gi\u1eef v\u1eefng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u1ef1c b\u1ea5t t\u00f2ng t\u00e2m, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Maroc ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 g\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng mang t\u00ean Ronaldo. T\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng Euro s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc Phi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (4-4-2):\u00a0<o:p></o:p>1. Patricio;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>21. Soares \u2013 3. Pepe \u2013 6. Fonte \u2013 5. Guerreiro;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>11. Silva \u2013 8. Moutinho \u2013 14. Carvalho \u2013 4. Fernandes;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>7. Ronaldo \u2013 17. Guedes<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Maroc (4-2-3-1):\u00a0<o:p></o:p>12. Mohamedi;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>2. Hakimi \u2013 5. Benatia \u2013 6. Saiss \u2013 3. Mendyl;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>14. Boussoufa \u2013 8. Ahmadi;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>7. Ziyech \u2013 10. Belhanda \u2013 18. Harit;\u00a0<o:p></o:p>9. Kaabi<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Maroc: 3-1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c (19h00 ng\u00e0y 206) \u00c1n t\u1eed \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Bo-Dao-Nha-vs-Maroc-(19h00-ngay-206)-An-tu-dau-tien-hinh-anh-4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha vs Mar\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/ronaldo-noi-gi-sau-cu-hattrick-vao-luoi-tay-ban-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-bo-dao-nha-33-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-188595.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 3-3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t La Roja h\u1ed7n mang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o VCK World Cup 2018 ch\u00fat n\u1eefa l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Seleccao \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"371","checkdouble":"188986"},{"date":"07:12 20/06","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/goc-nhin-salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-o-liverpool.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, NHM \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua. Tuy nhi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Salah l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Salah ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i 100% phong \u0111\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea3 vai kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng b\u1edfi &lsquo;\u0111\u00f4 v\u1eadt&rsquo; Sergio Ramos trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft UEFA Champions League 2017/18 di\u1ec5n ra h\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 5 v\u1eeba qua, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-ai-cap-vs-uruguay-tran-dau-bang-a-world-cup-2018-421-188574.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span>, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t khu\u00f4n m\u1eb7t th\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 trong th\u00e2m t\u00e2m anh r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi toan t\u00ednh c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Salah n\u00f3 c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho th\u1eddi gian anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u0169ng v\u1eaby \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u1edf n\u00ean ng\u1eafn l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 \u1edf Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u1ee9u tinh c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y,&nbsp;HLV H\u00e9ctor C\u00faper \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Salah t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn h\u01a1n cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi, m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi n\u1ed7i t\u1ec7. Hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thay phi\u00ean nhau ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng, g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u00ean h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-ai-cap-421-188956.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Ai C\u1eadp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m. Pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 pha x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u00f3ng th\u00f4ng minh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi xoay ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Salah. Tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 bu\u1ed9c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, do m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00ean Salah \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 &lsquo;sung&rsquo;. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 4 c\u00fa s\u00fat, 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. Salah ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t do ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o ra. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i pressing \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn &lsquo;Messi Ai C\u1eadp&rsquo; m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t trong su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp, v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn The Pharaohs ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>V\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Liverpool <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Salah t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc cho m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh trong l\u00e0ng t\u00fac c\u1ea7u gi\u00e1o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi Salah s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3ng vai &lsquo;Ch\u00faa c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf&rsquo; gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Liverpool trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Goc-nhin-Salah-tro-lai-nhung-sao-khong-the-loi-hai-nhu-tai-Liverpool-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM v\u1eabn \u0111ang m\u01a1 Salah s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o c\u00f9ng Liverpool tuy nhi\u00ean Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 khi ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0a The Kop v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League danh gi\u00e1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, Salah \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngang ng\u1eeda. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng gi\u00fap anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Liverpool, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Salah kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia. V\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e0 Salah \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018-461-188983.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-nga-31-ai-cap-bang-a-world-cup-2018-461-188983.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 3-1 Ai C\u1eadp (B\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u00e2\u0301t ba\u0323i 1-3 khi\u00ea\u0301n \u0110T Ai C\u00e2\u0323p g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 bi\u0323 loa\u0323i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, trong khi \u0111o\u0301 \u0111\u00f4\u0323i chu\u0309 nha\u0300 Nga g\u00e2\u0300n nh\u01b0 \u0111a\u0303 gia\u0300nh t\u00e2\u0301m ve\u0301 va\u0300o vo\u0300ng 1/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep-465-188982.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/thua-nga-mohamed-salah-va-ai-cap-van-con-co-hoi-di-tiep-465-188982.html\">Thua th\u1ea3m Nga, k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga, \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup-469-188985.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huy-diet-ai-cap-nga-lap-ky-luc-vo-tien-khoang-hau-o-world-cup-469-188985.html\">H\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Ai C\u1eadp, Nga l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu \u1edf World Cup</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u0103ng hoa sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu t\u1ea1i World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"370","checkdouble":"188989"},{"date":"07:28 20/06","title":"Ba Lan thua \u0111au Senegal b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/ba-lan-thua-dau-senegal-boi-su-yeu-kem-cua-trong-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho Senegal \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb pha c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng \"b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh\" c\u1ee7a Niang t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan, l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">2 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H \u0111\u1ec1u mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng Colombia, ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Senegal \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan b\u1eb1ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Ban-thang-cua-Niang-tran-Ba-Lan-vs-Senegal-khong-hop-le-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho ph\u00e9p Niang v\u00e0o s\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. \u1ea2nh: Daily Mail.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\r\nS\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba \u0111en, Senegal g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho &ldquo;\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng tr\u1eafng&rdquo;. Trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Szczesny v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00e0ng n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Senegal khi Niang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u00e0o ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 60. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Szczesny \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n non c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Song Niang, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A, b\u1ea5t th\u00ecnh l\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nH\u00f3a ra, sau khi \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbaye Niang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i cho ph\u00e9p ch\u1ea1y v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Ba Lan, anh &quot;l\u00e9n l\u00fat&quot; di chuy\u1ec3n ra sau l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u00e0 theo lu\u1eadt ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Niang nhanh chong ap vao cuop bong tu hang thu cua Ba Lan. Anh: AP.\" title=\"Niang nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ba Lan. \u1ea2nh: AP.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/aq.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Niang nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u1eadp v\u00e0o c\u01b0\u1edbp b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Ba Lan. \u1ea2nh: AP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5 ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tranh c\u00e3i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. \u0110a ph\u1ea7n \u00fd ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t, t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai s\u00f3t c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng ch\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nguy hi\u1ec3m. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Fox n\u00f3i: &quot;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n th\u00ec m\u1edbi cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n&quot;. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n M\u1ef9, Alexi Lalas \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Niang gi\u00fap Senegal v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ba Lan c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 1-2 \u1edf ph\u00fat 86, tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbt v\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-tang-boc-man-ra-quan-hoan-hao-cua-senegal-469-188981.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o c\u1ee7a Senegal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-ba-lan-12-senegal-421-188976.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ba Lan 1-2 Senegal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-aliou-cisse-chia-se-sau-tran-thang-cua-dt-senegal-465-188975.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Ba Lan, HLV \u0110T Senegal t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o ch\u00e2u Phi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-senegal-danh-bai-ba-lan-465-188973.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Senegal khi\u1ebfn Lewandowski im ti\u1ebfng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"369","checkdouble":"188991"},{"date":"07:32 20/06","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (20/6/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-2062018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 20/6 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.7.2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 20-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 20-6-2018 v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.v